{"tid":1875251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到咗社區大爆發 感染者被活捉 射殺燒死嘅階段 香港人會反抗嗎?","createTime":"2020-02-11T16:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T16:22:01.000Z","uid":35857,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"02bd57afe41d0789355a084eb3fcf0ed8480ed25","tid":1875251,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:07:24.000Z","msg":"隻病毒傳染性高<br />\n只係轉機嘅時間已經賴野<br />\n一個人中 一家人仆街<br />\n遲下社區爆發真係可能變到《流感》套戲咁<br />\n<br />\n成日話攬炒攬炒<br />\n諗住乜都唔做 等疫症發大 就攬炒到?<br />\n你真心覺得班黑警咁易中招咩?<br />\n成身高級防護裝 點中?<br />\n有咩事 林鄭一定死攬佢地<br />\n比晒啲資源佢地㗎喎<br />\n攬炒不成 反而自己人出晒事啦<br />\n<br />\n究竟去到嗰一刻<br />\n香港人會唔會反抗?<br />\n定係等封城 懷疑感染嘅人死晒 同自己人攬炒算?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好撚擔心 唔係擔心疫症發展成點<br />\n係擔心香港人唔爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603af10920bc23eef0574fb000bca0fa178e641d","tid":1875251,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"一樣唔會反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c466d2b71719464970ed688ad5ef411d7e7fc27b","tid":1875251,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"603af10920bc23eef0574fb000bca0fa178e641d","tid":1875251,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"一樣唔會反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"喺隔離營到求饒? 篤鳩身邊嗰個賴咗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b8b30a76ee5db4c04935d49ab14c702ab44dd4","tid":1875251,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:12:41.000Z","msg":"梗係唔會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hk